 A24确认《Talk To Me》续集《Talk 2 Me》 https://www.nme.com/news/film/a24-confirm-talk-to-me-sequel-talk-2-me-3480338?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=a24-confirm-talk-to-me-续集谈话 2-我Will RichardsWed, 09 Aug 2023 08:15:42 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3480338 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="跟我说话" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>热门恐怖片的原创编剧和导演团队将回归第二轮</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/a24-confirm-talk-to-me-sequel-talk-2-me-3480338">A24 确认《Talk To Me》续集《Talk 2 Me》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="跟我说话" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Talk_To_Me_Horror-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> A24 已确认热门恐怖电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/talk-to-me-review-horror-3474833"><em>《Talk To Me》</em></a>的续集正在制作中，名为<em>《Talk 2 Me》</em> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/talk-to-me-review-horror-3474833">《跟我说话》评论：为这部令人毛骨悚然的恐怖片首映提供帮助</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部澳大利亚电影于上个月上映，讲述了一位年轻女子米娅（苏菲·王尔德饰）在与一只经过防腐处理的手举行降神会后卷入超自然现象以及随之而来的恐怖故事的故事。</p><p> <em>《对我说话》</em>由丹尼和迈克尔·菲利波执导，这是他们的导演处女作，亚历山德拉·詹森饰演杰德，乔·伯德饰演莱利，奥蒂斯·丹吉饰演丹尼尔，米兰达·奥托饰演苏，佐伊·特拉克斯饰演海莉，克里斯·阿洛西奥饰演乔斯。</p><p>这部电影讲述了一群青少年在降神会时获得一只木乃伊手的故事，据说这只手可以将他们与灵魂联系起来。当连接到手上的时间不超过 90 秒时，用户会体验到毒品般的快感，导致青少年轮流使用它。</p><p>现在，已经确定菲利普兄弟将回归执导续集，您可以看下面的公告。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CvsH2MRNXfy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.8