-parenting-and-gender-identity-3480132">Ne-Yo 就有关育儿和性别认同的评论做出道歉的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《奥本海默》现在是有史以来最成功的二战电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-is-now-the-most-successful-ww2-film-ever-3480129?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=oppenheimer-is-now-the-most-成功的二战电影Will RichardsTue, 08 Aug 2023 19:14:33 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3480129 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《奥本海默》中的希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>克里斯托弗·诺兰的传记片全球票房已突破 5 亿美元</p><p>后《奥本海默》现在是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次上映的<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-is-now-the-most-successful-ww2-film-ever-3480129">​​最成功的二战电影</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《奥本海默》中的希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer">《奥本海默》</a></em>的全球票房已超过 5 亿美元（3.92 亿英镑），成为有史以来最成功的二战电影。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">《奥本海默》评论：克里斯托弗·诺兰令人兴奋的传记片像一颗炸弹一样击中大脑</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>广受好评的电影中饰演罗伯特·J·奥本海默，一位现实生活中的美国物理学家，在原子弹的制造过程中发挥了关键作用。</p><p>上周末，这部电影突破了巨大的票房里程碑，目前总票房达到 5.529 亿美元。</p><p>根据<a class="class" href="https://www.boxofficemojo.com/chart/top_lifetime_gross/?area=XWW" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Box Office Mojo 的</a>统计，该片超越<em>《敦刻尔克</em>》（5.27 亿美元）、 <em>《拯救大兵瑞恩》</em> （4.82 亿美元）和<em>《珍珠港》</em> （4.49 亿美元），成为以二战为背景的有史以来票房最高的电影。</p><p>然而，它仍然落后于其票房竞争对手<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie">《芭比娃娃》</a></em> ，后者本周末<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-has-hit-1billion-at-the-global-box-office-3478941">全球票房达到 10 亿美元</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3470626" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3470626" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3470626" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg" alt="奥本海默" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3470626" class="wp-caption-text"> 《奥本海默》中的希里安·墨菲。信用：环球</figcaption></figure><p><em>《奥本海默》</em>一经上映就获得了<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">五星级好评</a>，保罗·布拉德肖 (Paul Bradshaw) 写道：“<em>奥本海默</em>不仅是对原子弹背后的人的权威描述，也是成人电影制作领域的一项里程碑式的成就。多年来，诺兰一直在完善严肃大片的艺术——制作巧妙、精心调整、引人注目的多厅史诗片；除了在电影院之外，无法不间断、不受干扰地观看这些内容。但不知何故，这感觉更大。”</p><p>墨菲最近在接受<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/cillian-murphy-interview-oppenheimer-3470442"><em>NME</em></a>独家采访时解释了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-reveals-impact-of-ukraine-invasion-on-oppenheimer-cast-3478337">俄罗斯入侵乌克兰对</a><em>奥本海默</em>演员阵容的影响。</p><p>墨菲表示，演员们非常了解乌克兰发生的事件，特别是在俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)通过在其边境布设战术核导弹来回应国际制裁之后。</p><p> “它无处不在，我们完全意识到这一点，”墨菲谈到入侵时说道。 “自 1945 年以来，[核战争]的威胁多年来不断升级和消退……现在又卷土重来。它始终存在，这<a href="https://www.history.com/news/what-was-the-sword-of-damocles" target="_blank" rel="noopener">把达摩克利斯之剑</a>悬在我们头顶。”</p><p>后《奥本海默》现在是<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次上映的<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-is-now-the-most-successful-ww2-film-ever-3480129">​​最成功的二战电影</a>。</p> ;
